OL,3,CBan on disposable vapes has come into
OL,4,Cforce
OL,6,FDisposable vapes are now banned in
OL,7,FWales.
OL,9,FThe new law - which is in place across
OL,10,Fthe UK - came into effect 1 June and
OL,11,Fwill prohibit the sale of single use
OL,12,Fvapes.
OL,14,FThe law will be applied to businesses
OL,15,Fnot individuals, meaning that it will
OL,16,Fbe a criminal offence to sell or
OL,17,Fsupply disposable vapes but it will
OL,18,Fnot be illegal for people to use them
OL,19,Ffor personal use.
