OL,3,CBan on disposable vapes has come into
OL,4,Cforce
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government says the ban has
OL,7,Fbeen introduced to reduce the
OL,8,Fenvironmental harm caused by their
OL,9,Fproduction and incorrect disposal.
OL,11,FEnvironmental charity Keep Wales Tidy
OL,12,Festimates that over just one year,
OL,13,F360,000 single use vapes are littered
OL,14,Fon the ground in Wales, while 120,000
OL,15,Fare flushed down the toilet.
OL,17,FRogue traders who continue to sell
OL,18,Fthem risk a fine of #200 in the first
OL,19,Finstance, followed by an unlimited
OL,20,Ffine or jail time for repeat offending.
