OL,3,CBan on disposable vapes has come into
OL,4,Cforce
OL,6,FPublic Health Wales has welcomed the
OL,7,Fban.
OL,9,FThe health body says that there is a
OL,10,F"clear consensus" among health experts
OL,11,Fthat the availability and marketing of
OL,12,Fdisposable vape products has driven a
OL,13,Fsignificant rise in vaping among
OL,14,Fchildren and young people.
OL,16,FThey say around 16% of year eleven
OL,17,Fpupils regularly use vapes and nearly
OL,18,Fhalf have tried vaping. Of these, most
OL,19,Fhad never smoked before taking up
OL,20,Fvaping.
