OL,3,CBan on disposable vapes has come into
OL,4,Cforce
OL,6,FWhile the majority of single-use vapes
OL,7,Fcontain nicotine, the ban will also
OL,8,Fapply to nicotine free disposable
OL,9,Fvapes.
OL,11,FVapes now need to be refillable,
OL,12,Frechargeable, and have a replaceable
OL,13,Fcoil.
OL,15,FDeputy First Minister, with
OL,16,Fresponsibility for Climate Change, Huw
OL,17,FIrranca-Davies said: "Single-use vapes
OL,18,Fcreate litter and plastic pollution;
OL,19,Fthis ban will help stop the serious
OL,20,Fharm these products cause to our
OL,21,Fwildlife and environment.
