OL,3,CBan on disposable vapes has come into
OL,4,Cforce
OL,6,F"They should be recycled at a vape
OL,7,Fshop, or taken to a local authority
OL,8,Frecycling centre, to be disposed of
OL,9,Fsafely. Vapes should never go in the
OL,10,Fbin as they are susceptible to
OL,11,Fcatching fire."
OL,13,FMinister for Mental Health and
OL,14,FWellbeing, Sarah Murphy added: "In
OL,15,Faddition to the environmental impacts,
OL,16,Fwe know single-use vapes are being
OL,17,Fused by children and young people and
OL,18,Fare a factor in the significant
OL,19,Fincreases in youth vaping that we have
OL,20,Fseen in recent years.
